#### Bee
<br/>

<img align="left" src="//code.org/images/bee.png" height="200" width="300" hspace="20">

You'll need to move the bee around to collect all the nectar and make all the honey. The units of nectar and honey needed for each puzzle are written in the lower right-hand corner of each flower or honeycomb.
